('AES ECB Penguin', 'An image was encrypted with AES-ECB. The encrypted file still shows the outline of the original.', 'crypto', 'easy', 100, 'cyberops{3cb_p3ngu1n_p4tt3rn}', ARRAY['ECB encrypts identical blocks to identical ciphertext', 'Try viewing the encrypted file as a bitmap'], ARRAY[10, 25], true),
